OL,6,FA "dangerous predator" who secretly
OL,7,Ffilmed himself raping unconscious
OL,8,Fwomen and sexually abusing children,
OL,9,Fhas been jailed for life.
OL,11,FNicholas Moxham, of Heaton Chapel in
OL,12,FStockport, recruited women as sex
OL,13,Fworkers after "loitering around
OL,14,Fhomeless shelters", police said, and
OL,15,Fthen abused, raped and filmed them.
OL,17,FThe 53-year-old was sentenced at
OL,18,FMinshull Crown Court to a minimum term
OL,19,Fof 22 years, along with an indefinite
OL,20,Fsexual harm prevention order and
OL,21,Findefinite notification requirements.
