OL,6,FTwo of his victims read out statements
OL,7,Fin court, telling Moxham: "You preyed
OL,8,Fon the vulnerable and I hope you're
OL,9,Fashamed for what you did."
OL,11,FAnother said: "Thank you for ruining
OL,12,Fmy life and destroying my trust in the
OL,13,Fhuman race."
OL,15,FMoxham's crimes have been described by
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Police and the
OL,17,FCrown Prosecution Service as "one of
OL,18,Fthe most horrific and upsetting cases".
