OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Lee Attenborough,
OL,7,Fof Stockport CID, said: "Moxham is a
OL,8,Fcontrolling and predatory sex offender
OL,9,Fwho thought he was untouchable,
OL,10,Fdenying his horrendous crimes right to
OL,11,Fthe very end, forcing his victims to
OL,12,Fgo through the ordeal of a trial."
OL,14,FDuring the pandemic In March 2020, he
OL,15,Foffered his home to six female sex
OL,16,Fworkers to use to entertain clients,
OL,17,Fand later also at a second address in
OL,18,FLongsight, Manchester.
