OL,6,FThe predator soon began controlling
OL,7,Fthem, arranging when they would see
OL,8,Fclients, what services they would
OL,9,Fprovide and how many men they would
OL,10,Fsee in a day.
OL,12,FHe controlled their money ` firstly by
OL,13,Ftaking money for petrol and expenses,
OL,14,Fthen taking more money as time went on
OL,15,Fand expecting to have sex with them
OL,16,Fwithout payment.
OL,18,FMoxham, 52, secretly recorded the
OL,19,Fwomen while they were with clients,
OL,20,Fsometimes selling the recordings and
OL,21,Fkeeping the money.
